{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2988770/extras/7gJe+S.png?t=1724259991\" /><br><br>After dying, poisoned for unknown reasons, Isobel finds herself in the afterlife... and on a dangerous mission. Experience the first part of a truly unique upcoming visual novel full of character, mystery and heart as you point and click your way to unveiling the strange world of Purgatory's many secrets in this expansive demo.<br><br><i>If you complete the demo, your progress can be restored in the upcoming full release of the game.</i><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2988770/extras/YpuoGAsmaller.png?t=1724259991\" /> <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2988770/extras/lwzqQa.png?t=1724259991\" /> <strong>Enjoy</strong> the prologue and entire first act (almost 100,000 words/5-10 hours of playtime) of the upcoming full game.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2988770/extras/lwzqQa.png?t=1724259991\" /> <strong>Explore</strong> the interactive world of Purgatory through a day-night cycle with four segments per day... lots of stuff to click on (or not, if you don't want to).<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2988770/extras/lwzqQa.png?t=1724259991\" /> <strong>Meet</strong> unforgettable characters, all with their own fleshed out personalities and agendas.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2988770/extras/lwzqQa.png?t=1724259991\" /> <strong>Stay</strong> connected to the Dwellers and Denizens of the afterlife via the PurgaPhone! Send and receive messages, with many of them unique to the choices you make.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2988770/extras/lwzqQa.png?t=1724259991\" /> <strong>Partake</strong> in two different character routes (the full game will have nine), as well as a number of exciting side stories that further develop the world, and watch as their outcomes change the main narrative in meaningful ways.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2988770/extras/lwzqQa.png?t=1724259991\" /> <strong>Marvel</strong> at sprites, backgrounds, special scenes and inventory items all drawn in a beautiful and unique style.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2988770/extras/lwzqQa.png?t=1724259991\" /> <strong>Unlock</strong> a wealth of hidden treasures, such as gallery images, music tracks and encyclopedia entries.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2988770/extras/lwzqQa.png?t=1724259991\" /> <strong>Bop</strong> your head to a dynamic soundtrack composed by popular YouTube artist Endigo.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2988770/extras/pQFG50.png?t=1724259991\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2988770/extras/isobelbio.png?t=1724259991\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2988770/extras/blissbio.png?t=1724259991\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2988770/extras/sheolbio.png?t=1724259991\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2988770/extras/apechsbio.png?t=1724259991\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2988770/extras/remmbio.png?t=1724259991\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://